steps.name: Navigate to Home Page and Accept cookies
Wait for selector getByRole('button', { name: 'Accept All Cookies' })
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('heading', { name: 'Save 20% on travel internet' })
Navigate to Europe Region Plans Page
Select a plan in Europe Region and Go to Checkout
Proceed to Checkout from Cart Page
Fill Personal Details for exisiting user
Fill Billing Details for user
